 "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1607656854", "stars": 4360, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "TripleZ", "website": "blog.triplez.cn", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8632a37f1bf7777a0658c8d8a0293b7e?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/TripleZ", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1530163969, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8632a37f1bf7777a0658c8d8a0293b7e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8632a37f1bf7777a0658c8d8a0293b7e?s=24&d=retro", "location": "Shenzhen, P.R. China", "btc": "", "id": 325377}, "last_reply_by": "Tumblr", "last_touched": 1627138627, "title": "macOS 下有什么快速切换窗口的方法吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/791480", "created": 1627096152, "content": "macOS 下按 Cmd+Tab 显示出来的是不同的软件切换。但如果一个软件有多个实例（比如开了两个 vscode 项目），多个实例又在多个桌面上（两个 vscode ）在不同桌面上，软件切换的方式就没法切换到目标窗口了。\r\n\r\nWindows 下的切换是以实例为粒度的，请问各位 macOS 下有类似的解决方案吗？", "content_rendered": "macOS 下按 Cmd+Tab 显示出来的是不同的软件切换。但如果一个软件有多个实例（比如开了两个 vscode 项目），多个实例又在多个桌面上（两个 vscode ）在不同桌面上，软件切换的方式就没法切换到目标窗口了。<br /><br />Windows 下的切换是以实例为粒度的，请问各位 macOS 下有类似的解决方案吗？", "last_modified": 1627096152, "replies": 21, "id": 791480}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1627019971", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1627019971", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 11824, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1627019971", "stars": 2098, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"username": "yycf", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8016d6fdf401ec58d654620af437e075?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yycf", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1487740936, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8016d6fdf401ec58d654620af437e075?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8016d6fdf401ec58d654620af437e075?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 216623}, "last_reply_by": "yycf", "last_touched": 1627147198, "title": "在武汉 18k， 上海 28k 的 offer 去不去？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/791555", "created": 1627139118, "content": "请问这是相当于降薪了吗？", "content_rendered": "<p>请问这是相当于降薪了吗？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1627139118, "replies": 20, "id": 791555}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1622572533", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1622572533", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 174768, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533", "stars": 3282, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"username": "ooyy", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ae73/c1ed/76340_mini.png?m=1614308646", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/ooyy", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1412784415, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ae73/c1ed/76340_mini.png?m=1614308646", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ae73/c1ed/76340_mini.png?m=1614308646", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 76340}, "last_reply_by": "jayvs5200", "last_touched": 1627139368, "title": "AdGuard 的过滤规则请教", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/791501", "created": 1627106841, "content": "现在用的 AdGuard 作为家里神兽的网页浏览过滤方案\r\n\r\n使用的规则主要是域名和 URL 过滤，如下语法可以屏蔽搜索引擎的关键词“色情小说”\r\n```\r\n%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%B4$empty,domain=bing.com|baidu.com|google.com|so.com|sogou.com,important\r\n```\r\n但是如果 URL 中不含有这个词汇，就不能屏蔽了，比如通过网页上的链接打开。\r\n\r\n所以我希望能够从网页内容的 Title 里面搜索关键词，如果 Title 中有，就屏蔽整个页面的显示。\r\n\r\n研究它的规则一上午，没找到头绪，哪位大佬指点一下？", "content_rendered": "<p>现在用的 AdGuard 作为家里神兽的网页浏览过滤方案</p>\n<p>使用的规则主要是域名和 URL 过滤，如下语法可以屏蔽搜索引擎的关键词“色情小说”</p>\n<pre><code>%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E5%B0%8F%E8%AF%B4$empty,domain=bing.com|baidu.com|google.com|so.com|sogou.com,important\n</code></pre>\n<p>但是如果 URL 中不含有这个词汇，就不能屏蔽了，比如通过网页上的链接打开。</p>\n<p>所以我希望能够从网页内容的 Title 里面搜索关键词，如果 Title 中有，就屏蔽整个页面的显示。</p>\n<p>研究它的规则一上午，没找到头绪，哪位大佬指点一下？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1627106841, "replies": 17, "id": 791501}]